Actions.Text: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

Title: Establishes the city of Dunkirk interim finance authority
Summary: Establishes the city of Dunkirk interim finance authority; provides for its functions, powers and duties.
LawCode: Add Art 10-D Title 1-A §§3750 - 3772, Pub Auth L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public authorities law, in relation to establishing the city of Dunkirk interim finance authority
